      "type": "ValidationResult",
      "name": "PIV velocity field comparison — FDA pump benchmark",
      "description": "Simulated velocity magnitude fields compared against particle image velocimetry (PIV) measurements from the FDA pump interlaboratory study. Mean absolute error across 12 measurement planes is 4.2% of peak velocity. GCI-based discretization uncertainty is 2.8%.",
      "prov:wasDerivedFrom": "https://uofa.net/synth/evidence/fda-piv-interlaboratory-2021",
      "outcome": "Pass",
      "quantitativeMetric": "MAE = 4.2 % peak velocity; GCI = 2.8 %"
    },
    {
